Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.86,0:00:32.49,Default,,0,0,0,,In the ancient Greece, you can see that I'm an enthusiast of ancient Greece.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.30,0:00:38.14,Default,,0,0,0,,There's three things, logos, ethos, and pathos.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.20,0:00:41.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Logos is the integrity of the speaker.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.57,0:00:44.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Ethos is the integrity of the message.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.65,0:00:48.33,Default,,0,0,0,,And pathos is the receptivity of the audience.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.34,0:00:52.94,Default,,0,0,0,,And if you don't pay attention to all three, your message doesn't get across.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.25,0:00:54.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.44,0:00:59.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Logos, ethos, and pathos.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.76,0:01:02.18,Default,,0,0,0,,I know you were just dying to know that.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.18,0:01:08.46,Default,,0,0,0,,No, that's fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.89,0:01:14.57,Default,,0,0,0,,The receptivity of the audience.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.77,0:01:18.79,Default,,0,0,0,,So we're blessed to have such a receptive audience, you see.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.60,0:01:25.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Because if the audience is dumb, it doesn't do any good to be smart.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.44,0:01:29.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, golly.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.93,0:01:31.27,Default,,0,0,0,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.41,0:01:38.13,Default,,0,0,0,,So we have a – oh, thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.23,0:01:39.85,Default,,0,0,0,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.89,0:01:40.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you, God.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.43,0:01:41.69,Default,,0,0,0,,One rainy hour.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.97,0:01:42.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.40,0:01:48.24,Default,,0,0,0,,So we talked about, of course, the levels of consciousness is what we talk about all the time.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.31,0:01:51.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Adaptational stress to change.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.09,0:01:53.05,Default,,0,0,0,,There's a constant adaptational stress.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.96,0:01:57.58,Default,,0,0,0,,It's measurable physiologically and hormonally.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.40,0:02:02.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Any change brings about a stress and the release of stress hormones.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.05,0:02:08.91,Default,,0,0,0,,And some people really go into exhaustion, adrenal exhaustion.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.91,0:02:12.45,Default,,0,0,0,,So change is kind of stressful to the adrenal glands.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.16,0:02:14.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Adrenal glands put out.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.72,0:02:19.42,Default,,0,0,0,,That's cortisone, the alarm reaction, et cetera.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.78,0:02:28.60,Default,,0,0,0,,So when you have to change your whole lifestyle or you change due to age or some change in your physiology or physicality,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.40,0:02:30.60,Default,,0,0,0,,there's a certain strain.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.02,0:02:40.02,Default,,0,0,0,,So getting used to the world with one eye, for instance, one dim eye is a stress.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.02,0:02:46.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Some from binocular, you have to go to monocular.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.12,0:02:52.58,Default,,0,0,0,,And your memory track fills in what the rest of the image is like.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.76,0:02:56.30,Default,,0,0,0,,You know what wrong people look like because you saw a lot of wrong people.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.71,0:03:01.43,Default,,0,0,0,,So there's an adaptational stress to change.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.13,0:03:05.25,Default,,0,0,0,,And some people really – they really collapse in this level.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.47,0:03:06.71,Default,,0,0,0,,You see this very frequently.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.49,0:03:11.67,Default,,0,0,0,,People really collapse based on the stress of change.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.67,0:03:15.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Sometimes they go into adrenal exhaustion, adrenal exhaustion.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.06,0:03:19.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Adaptational stress to change.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.13,0:03:26.75,Default,,0,0,0,,We have to get used to the different forms of government and, of course, our government,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.75,0:03:32.47,Default,,0,0,0,,although its basic structure remains the same, it's really constantly changing its character.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.47,0:03:34.21,Default,,0,0,0,,It's constantly changing its character.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.93,0:03:38.87,Default,,0,0,0,,And what was appropriate at one time is no longer acceptable.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.82,0:03:46.29,Default,,0,0,0,,My father used to get into a big upset every night at dinner about Roosevelt.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.29,0:03:47.42,Default,,0,0,0,,He said, you know what?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.42,0:03:48.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Roosevelt and the New Deal.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.90,0:03:53.36,Default,,0,0,0,,And then there were the unions.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.46,0:03:54.72,Default,,0,0,0,,The unions were taking over.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.34,0:04:02.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, I can't remember whether he was on the side of the unions, the side of Roosevelt, or not.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.64,0:04:04.60,Default,,0,0,0,,He was very impassioned about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.34,0:04:06.90,Default,,0,0,0,,And it was every night at dinner.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.08,0:04:11.12,Default,,0,0,0,,My mother would – Raymond, Raymond, are you –
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.12,0:04:11.82,Default,,0,0,0,,God damn it.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.56,0:04:15.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Every night this would go on.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.86,0:04:16.54,Default,,0,0,0,,It was hysterical.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.18,0:04:18.70,Default,,0,0,0,,You'd be upset by something.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.82,0:04:20.74,Default,,0,0,0,,And night after night, this would go on.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.74,0:04:22.08,Default,,0,0,0,,And night after night, this went on for years.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.60,0:04:26.16,Default,,0,0,0,,And I can't remember whether he was pro-Roosevelt or anti-Roosevelt.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.70,0:04:30.20,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't remember which way it was.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.23,0:04:34.05,Default,,0,0,0,,I think he was incensed that the unions were taking over.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.67,0:04:36.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, it's because they were rioting.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.15,0:04:39.33,Default,,0,0,0,,The unions were – union riots.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.45,0:04:44.21,Default,,0,0,0,,So he was mad because they were – because he was a very law and order kind of a person.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.04,0:04:46.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, very law and order.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.55,0:04:51.49,Default,,0,0,0,,So, but adaptation will stretch the change.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.49,0:04:55.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Because the different forms of government, and certainly the Roosevelt era,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.13,0:04:57.93,Default,,0,0,0,,was a major change in government.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.56,0:05:01.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Accountability is responsibility.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.48,0:05:06.53,Default,,0,0,0,,And this is really central to all spiritual evolution.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.27,0:05:10.15,Default,,0,0,0,,You're either accountable for your answers or you're not.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.94,0:05:13.62,Default,,0,0,0,,If you're not – if you consider yourself not accountable,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.24,0:05:17.62,Default,,0,0,0,,you cannot do the muscle test for truth.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.08,0:05:24.34,Default,,0,0,0,,If you're not accountable, that negates the value of truth.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.34,0:05:24.42,Default,,0,0,0,,That's it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.82,0:05:25.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Does it not?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.98,0:05:30.58,Default,,0,0,0,,So those who negate the truth cannot do the test.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.04,0:05:35.06,Default,,0,0,0,,People below 200 don't – are unable to do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.24,0:05:37.88,Default,,0,0,0,,And to higher the level of consciousness,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.88,0:05:41.92,Default,,0,0,0,,which is research sent to me by Scott.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.04,0:05:44.58,Default,,0,0,0,,And this is Scott Jeffrey, an associate.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.50,0:05:47.54,Default,,0,0,0,,That as the level of consciousness goes up,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.80,0:05:51.36,Default,,0,0,0,,the percentage of correctness and calibrating levels increases.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.10,0:05:55.38,Default,,0,0,0,,And the optimal level for practicality,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.38,0:05:59.56,Default,,0,0,0,,would be about where this audience is, mid-400s or so.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.12,0:06:02.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Mid-400s is where people are intelligent,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.68,0:06:06.04,Default,,0,0,0,,integrous, accountable, take responsibility,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.92,0:06:09.88,Default,,0,0,0,,and are consciously evolving.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.41,0:06:16.31,Default,,0,0,0,,So accountability, then, is necessary.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.13,0:06:18.39,Default,,0,0,0,,To think you're not accountable,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.42,0:06:22.10,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know at the last moment on Earth
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.10,0:06:24.16,Default,,0,0,0,,what people think about this.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.16,0:06:25.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Ha, ha, ha.
